@host = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

### 1) 원천 데이터 저장
POST {{host}}/study/cachetier/data/product:100
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "value": "apple",
  "invalidateCaches": true
}

### 2) Cache-aside: 첫 조회는 loader, 다음 조회는 local cache
GET {{host}}/study/cachetier/cache-aside/product:100
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 3) Cache-aside: local cache hit
GET {{host}}/study/cachetier/cache-aside/product:100
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 4) LoadingCache: miss 시 Caffeine loader 자동 호출
GET {{host}}/study/cachetier/loading/product:100
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 5) refreshAfterWrite: refresh 대상 cache 조회
GET {{host}}/study/cachetier/refresh/product:100
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 6) 원천 데이터만 변경하고 cache는 유지
POST {{host}}/study/cachetier/data/product:100
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "value": "apple-v2",
  "invalidateCaches": false
}

### 7) refreshAfterWrite cache 수동 refresh
POST {{host}}/study/cachetier/refresh/product:100
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 8) cache-aside entry invalidate
POST {{host}}/study/cachetier/cache-aside/product:100/invalidate
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 9) cache stats
GET {{host}}/study/cachetier/cache-aside/stats
Accept: {{contentType}}
